video.title: Grace and Frankie
video.synopsis: Theyâ€™re not friends, but when their husbands leave them for each other, proper Grace and eccentric Frankie begin to bond in this Emmy-nominated series.

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie are stunned when their husbands inform them that they want divorces. They're even more stunned when they find out why.
episodes.title: The End

episodes.synopsis: The messy realities of divorce start to sink in for Grace, Frankie, Robert, Sol and their equally frazzled adult children.
episodes.title: The Credit Cards

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie decide to go back to work. Robert and Sol have an awkward dinner party for their children.
episodes.title: The Dinner

episodes.synopsis: Emotions run high when a funeral throws Grace, Frankie, Robert and Sol together in public for the first time since the split.
episodes.title: The Funeral

episodes.synopsis: Grace has an eye-opening experience when she goes out for frozen yogurt with Frankie and Brianna on a Saturday night.
episodes.title: The Fall

episodes.synopsis: Sol takes care of Frankie after she has an earthquake freak-out, while Grace goes on her first date. Coyote pays Mallory a surprise visit.
episodes.title: The Earthquake

episodes.synopsis: Frankie, Grace and Brianna have unexpected encounters when they try new ways to deal with being single.
episodes.title: The Spelling Bee

episodes.synopsis: Frankie takes a new look at her Yam Man Jacob, while Grace and Guy get closer. Bud and Coyote have a brotherly talk. Sol is terrified of Brianna.
episodes.title: The Sex

episodes.synopsis: Brianna tries Frankie's homemade organic beauty product. Robert finds out about Guy and Grace. Frankie tries to set boundaries with Sol.
episodes.title: The Invitation

episodes.synopsis: After they sign the divorce papers, Frankie, Grace, Sol, Robert and Bud remember a pivotal weekend from five years before.
episodes.title: The Elevator

episodes.synopsis: Grace tells Frankie a secret that Frankie shares with Sol, setting off multiple arguments in both houses. Brianna gets closer with a co-worker.
episodes.title: The Secrets

episodes.synopsis: Bud and Coyote ask Brianna and Mallory to help them throw Sol and Robert's bachelor party. Grace offers to do ANYTHING to cheer up Frankie.
episodes.title: The Bachelor Party

episodes.synopsis: As the wedding day approaches, Grace and Robert have problems expressing themselves, while Sol and Frankie finally clear out their old house.
episodes.title: The Vows

episodes.synopsis: Sol plans to tell Robert about his betrayal. Frankie is determined to finally separate emotionally from Sol, but events pull her back in.
episodes.title: The Wish

episodes.synopsis: Brianna, Mallory and Bud help Sol deal with wedding details. A visit to Robert and Sol's house brings up strong emotions for Grace and Frankie.
episodes.title: The Vitamix

episodes.synopsis: Brianna wants to produce Frankie's organic yam lube. Grace competes for her grandchildren's affection. Frankie reconnects with her Yam Man, Jacob.
episodes.title: The Negotiation

episodes.synopsis: Frankie tracks down Grace's former love Phil on the internet, and the two set off to find him. Tensions arise between Sol and Robert.
episodes.title: The Road Trip

episodes.synopsis: Frankie has difficulty passing the test to renew her driver's license. Grace attempts to amp up her social life by reconnecting with old friends.
episodes.title: The Test

episodes.synopsis: While Grace mentors a young woman seeking a new career, Frankie has conflicted feelings for Jacob, who wants more than a business relationship.
episodes.title: The Chicken

episodes.synopsis: Grace intervenes after Robert and Sol's big fight. Frankie opens up to Jacob. An online friend request from Phil surprises Grace.
episodes.title: The Boar

episodes.synopsis: Frankie has issues with Brianna's ideas for her yam lube and makes a stand. Phil asks Grace out for lunch. Sol tries to work things out with Robert.
episodes.title: The Anchor

episodes.synopsis: Coyote shares some surprising news. Things go awry when Frankie and Sol host a family brunch. Grace must make a difficult decision about Phil.
episodes.title: The Goodbyes

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Phil get closer, but complications arise. Sol and Robert square off on opposite sides of the conflict between Frankie and Brianna.
episodes.title: The Loophole

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie nurse their emotional wounds: Frankie performs a ritual on the beach, and Grace goes out drinking. Bud and Coyote meet Jacob.
episodes.title: The Bender

episodes.synopsis: As Frankie helps her old friend Babe plan a big bash, she's faced with a troubling decision. Grace tries to make amends to Frankie.
episodes.title: The Party

episodes.synopsis: Frankie and Grace receive surprise gifts from Babe that open new horizons for each of them. Sol reveals a long-held secret at Bud's birthday party.
episodes.title: The Coup

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie try to get a bank loan to help start their new business. Frankie's art show is rife with family tensions and minor dramas.
episodes.title: The Art Show

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie pitch their business plan at a hip startup incubator. Grace fights with Jacob. Sol and Robert play hooky from work.
episodes.title: The Incubator

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie put together a focus group to test their vibrator prototype, but things go awry. Robert and Sol audition for a play.
episodes.title: The Focus Group

episodes.synopsis: After they're robbed, Frankie is rattled, but Grace has a secret. With Robert in rehearsals and making new friends, Sol feels left out.
episodes.title: The Burglary

episodes.synopsis: Furious about Grace's revelation, Frankie refuses to make up with her. In the wake of his fight with Sol, Robert decides to come out to his mother.
episodes.title: The Gun

episodes.synopsis: Frankie refuses to go home, and all the kids are dragged into Grace and Frankie's fight. Grace, Brianna and Mallory smoke Frankie's pot together.
episodes.title: The Pot

episodes.synopsis: The ladies hurt their backs and canâ€™t get off the floor. Coyote looks for a new home. Robert frets over unresolved issues with his mom.
episodes.title: The Floor

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie launch their business, and Bud brings gifts they're reluctant to accept. Sol is upset that Bud wants to fire a longtime employee.
episodes.title: The Alert

episodes.synopsis: Jacob shares something with Frankie that upsets her. Everyone rallies around Robert when his mother dies. Mallory confides in Brianna.
episodes.title: The Apology

episodes.synopsis: Sol and Robert pitch in when Grace and Frankie are overwhelmed with orders. Bud is thrown for a loop by his girlfriendâ€™s interest in the MÃ©nage Ã  Moi.
episodes.title: The Labels

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie send a cease and desist letter to the company that stole their idea. A homophobic church group protests Robert's play rehearsals.
episodes.title: The Other Vibrator

episodes.synopsis: Grace wants Frankie to go to the hospital after a medical incident, but Frankie insists on alternative healing. The protests disrupt Robert's play.
episodes.title: The Musical

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie face a lawsuit. Sol fights back against the homophobic play protesters. Frankie mulls over a move that would change everything.
episodes.title: The Sign

episodes.synopsis: Frankie feels left out of Grace's friendship with Sheree, her new lodger. Sol and Robert are arrested. Bud and Allison throw a gender-reveal party.
episodes.title: The Lodger

episodes.synopsis: Frankie shares what she discovered about Sheree to a skeptical Grace. Bud sends everyone on a scavenger hunt. Frankie makes a big decision.
episodes.title: The Scavengender Hunt

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie try to help Sheree get her house back ... using both legal and illegal methods. Robert is nominated for a Tappy acting award.
episodes.title: The Tappys

episodes.synopsis: Grace fears her relationship has reached its expiration date. Frankie faces an existential crisis when she learns she's been declared legally dead.
episodes.title: The Expiration Date

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie hold vibrator pop-up sales at a senior center and a college. Sol and Robert have a disagreement. Bud and Allison hit a roadblock.
episodes.title: The Pop-Ups

episodes.synopsis: Frankie reconnects with someone important from her past. Despite problems with her knee, Grace refuses to slow down. Robert tries to make amends.
episodes.title: The Hinge

episodes.synopsis: Frankie and Sol have a blast devising a plan to get Frankie declared legally alive again. Grace faces some truths at a funeral she attends with Robert.
episodes.title: The Landline

episodes.synopsis: Frankie convinces Allison to have a home birth. Grace and Frankie wind up stuck with a bickering Robert and Sol when there's a neighborhood lockdown.
episodes.title: The Lockdown

episodes.synopsis: Nick helps Grace while she's recovering from surgery. Jacob gets upset with Frankie because she wants to spend all their couple time with the baby.
episodes.title: The Knee

episodes.synopsis: Robert and Sol begin therapy. Grace and Frankie get a surprise when they bring gifts to a fan of their vibrators. Brianna's nemesis makes an offer.
episodes.title: The Death Stick

episodes.synopsis: Grace hires a contractor to fix an issue at the beach house. Sol's new friendship makes Robert uncomfortable. Frankie gets lost with the baby.
episodes.title: The Tub

episodes.synopsis: As Grace and Frankie deal with a major disaster in their home, they each keep secrets from other family members. Everyone attends Robert's play.
episodes.title: The Rats

episodes.synopsis: Prompted by their children, Grace and Frankie make a change. Robert and Sol channel some fresh energy into their marriage.
episodes.title: The Home

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie visit the beach house while their worried kids try to track them down. Robert and Sol are caught in an embarrassing situation.
episodes.title: The House

episodes.synopsis: Refusing to leave the beach house, Grace and Frankie get support from their ex-husbands -- who are having their own issues with an unexpected visitor.
episodes.title: The Squat

episodes.synopsis: Bud convinces Frankie to hire a home health aide. Grace fumes when she learns about Briannaâ€™s changes to Say Grace. Robert hopes to influence Peter.
episodes.title: The Aide

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Brianna clash at work as Grace faces a tough day. With Joan-Margaret's help, Frankie fights ageism. Peter's casting decision shocks Robert.
episodes.title: The Crosswalk

episodes.synopsis: An unexpected encounter sparks regret in Grace. Sol acts cagey about his new dog's origins. A stranger's ambush of Coyote leads to a revelation.
episodes.title: The Pharmacy

episodes.synopsis: Frankie takes Grace on a girls trip, which isn't exactly the spa retreat Grace was expecting. Mallory goes on a date. An old friend rebuffs Frankie.
episodes.title: The Retreat

episodes.synopsis: While Frankie worries she's lost her authenticity, Grace frets about Frankie's health. Bud's first meeting with Allison's father goes downhill fast.
episodes.title: The Tremor

episodes.synopsis: Robert feels out of place with the younger guys at rehearsals. Grace doesn't like the new man in Frankie's life. Brianna must make a difficult choice.
episodes.title: The Ceremony

episodes.synopsis: When the Vybrant website goes down, Grace and Frankie must negotiate with a demanding man from Walden Villas. Sol becomes more assertive.
episodes.title: The Website

episodes.synopsis: Grace takes extreme measures to keep up her hectic schedule. Sol and Frankie have a disagreement about Coyote. Frankie bonds with Robert over edibles.
episodes.title: The Highs

episodes.synopsis: While Frankie tries to dig herself out of the business mess she created, Grace comes up with a different solution. Brianna goes to bat for Barry.
episodes.title: The Video

episodes.synopsis: Grace returns to town to find that Frankie has everything under control. Bud and Allison's wedding day arrives, but not without some family drama.
episodes.title: The Wedding

episodes.synopsis: In the wake of their big fight, Grace and Frankie imagine what their lives would be like if they hadn't lived together for the last three years.
episodes.title: The Alternative

episodes.synopsis: Frankie is stunned by Grace's news, but she buries her feelings -- until everyone gathers together to send off Bud and Allison.
episodes.title: The Newlyweds

episodes.synopsis: While Frankie tries to adjust to living alone, Grace arranges a family dinner that takes an awkward turn. Robert and Sol plan a honeymoon trip.
episodes.title: The Rescue

episodes.synopsis: Grace's insecurities flare at a lavish fundraiser, where Frankie gets swept up in a silent auction. Sol hosts a game night to distract a worried Robert.
episodes.title: The Trophy Wife

episodes.synopsis: Robert and Sol grapple with a health scare, while Grace's bad knee sparks a new business idea. Coyote connects with Bud's ex-girlfriend.
episodes.title: The Funky Walnut

episodes.synopsis: Grace worries that Nick isn't satisfied with their sex life. Sol decides to keep his diagnosis a secret, and Coyote comes clean about Jessica.
episodes.title: The Confessions

episodes.synopsis: Robert's fussing irritates Sol. Barry presses Brianna and Mallory to make up. Frankie's date with Jack inspires a marketing strategy for the Rise Up.
episodes.title: The Bad Hearer

episodes.synopsis: Grace wants to leverage Jack's celebrity connections ... and Sol and Robert realize they've met him before. Bud tries to prove he's over Jessica.
episodes.title: The Surprises

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie introduce Jack to Nick, hoping they can all go on vacation together. Meanwhile, Barry finally gets his short-rib double date.
episodes.title: The Short Rib

episodes.synopsis: Frankie's enjoying having two men in her life, but Grace warns her it won't end well. Allison and Sol encourage Bud to get a DNA test.
episodes.title: The One-At-A-Timing

episodes.synopsis: Grace's plan for a relaxing spa day backfires. Frankie tries to find Joan-Margaret a husband. Robert hosts a fundraiser to save the community theater.
episodes.title: The Scent

episodes.synopsis: Grace and Frankie prepare for their pitch, but their prototype is missing. Robert keeps a secret from Sol. Brianna gets an appealing offer.
episodes.title: The Laughing Stock

episodes.synopsis: Grace's loyalties are tested as she and Frankie face the Sharks. Robert scrambles to recoup the money he donated. Bud meets his long-lost cousin.
episodes.title: The Tank

episodes.synopsis: Grace tries to make amends to Frankie, Sol gives Robert a taste of his own medicine, and Brianna and Barry reach a turning point in their relationship.
episodes.title: The Change

episodes.synopsis: With their exes living at the beach house and FBI agents who arrested Nick sniffing around, Grace and Frankie frantically search for the money they hid.
episodes.title: The Roomies

episodes.synopsis: While Frankie retrieves the cash, Grace and Nick discuss their marriage at his arraignment. Joan-Margaret hatches a plan for laundering the money.
episodes.title: The Arraignment

episodes.synopsis: Bud tries to soothe discord at the beach house by throwing a brunch for the two families. But revelations from the past create even more hard feelings.
episodes.title: The Bunny

episodes.synopsis: Nick has a chance to get out of jail, but Grace likes things the way they are. An old acquaintance helps Frankie with the money laundering.
episodes.title: The Circumcision
